      <div class="subfield"><strong>$d - Volumes/dates to which call number applies</strong> <div class="description">Those items in the series to which the call number applies. Used when the call
                              number does not apply to all items of the series. The field is repeated to record
                              varying call numbers for different ranges of volumes/dates within a series or
                           set.
         </div>
