      <div class="subfield"><strong>$z - Canceled/invalid call number</strong> <div class="description">Document call number that has been canceled or determined to be invalid by the
                              authoritative agency. Subfield $z is repeated for multiple canceled or
                              invalid call numbers.
         </div>
