         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$2 - Number source</strong> <div class="description">MARC code that identifies the government document classification system or scheme
                              when the first indicator position contains value blank (#). Code from: <em><a href="http://www.loc.gov/standards/sourcelist/classification.html">Classification Scheme Source Codes</a></em>.
         </div>
